{"word":"Balaam","slug":"balaam","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Balaam</b> <a href=\"#/H1109\">H1109</a><br/><a href=\"#/G903\">G903</a> <br/> Son of Beor.<br/> From Mesopotamia<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=4'>Deu 23:4</a><br/> A soothsayer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=22'>Jos 13:22</a><br/> A prophet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=24&verse=9'>Num 24:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=2&verse=16'>2Pe 2:16</a><br/> Balak sends for, to curse Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=22&verse=7'>Num 22:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=9'>Jos 24:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=2'>Neh 13:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=6&verse=5'>Mic 6:5</a><br/> Anger of, rebuked by his ass<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=22&verse=35'>Num 22:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=2&verse=16'>2Pe 2:16</a><br/> Counsel of an occasion of Israel's corruption with the Midianites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=16'>Num 31:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=2&verse=15'>Rev 2:15</a><br/> Covetousness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=2&verse=15'>2Pe 2:15</a>; <a href='B:'></a><br/> Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=8'>Num 31:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=22'>Jos 13:22</a>"}]}